4d:["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":["If a plugin’s ",["$","code",null,{"className":"nextra-code","dir":"ltr","children":"install()"}]," throws, the error is caught and logged. The plugin is not installed, but the server continues."]}]
